{"tid":1420143,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"**有新又簡單方法** 唔需要割 亦唔需要行動降級 去提升民意","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:10:40.000Z","uid":221856,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8f045c72e09564dc72c6e83e77cd0ffd53ec42a8","tid":1420143,"uid":221856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:50:31.000Z","msg":"文宣 廣傳 e.g. winter on fire等歷實資訊 出去<br />\n比和理非同淺黃淺藍 就可以了<br />\n<br />\n有部份中立/ 外國人最近都講明, 其實就算而家咁既行動, 係外國都係好小兒科...<br />\n所以比和理非同淺黃淺藍知道外國係點示威, 佢地自然會比較香港示威者係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自然唔會失民意, 公道自在人心<br />\n因為...香港示威者真係好和平, 呢個全球公認的<br />\n<br />\n有巴打指而家已經唔需要理會民意, 小弟有保留的<br />\n如果可以一邊行動, 一邊保留/增加民意, 何樂而不為呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外, 文宣方面, 尋日罷工成果要攪攪佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多人連幾多人罷都唔知"},{"pid":"b032fda6371c4943a01c00cfaae3bd75ed7d98cf","tid":1420143,"uid":221856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:51:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ec8f0b3c4124c23aa2040b6bc01af4d6d996e4d","tid":1420143,"uid":221856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:51:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"603edb7f60f721e94332090e49b5d5ffe667b4d1","tid":1420143,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"畀返大陸釣魚台示威佢地睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5dc83f1f93a7a449a8548557b180c9a4511ada","tid":1420143,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3e7966e256282d9686a2e08129aa595c866846","tid":1420143,"uid":221856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"603edb7f60f721e94332090e49b5d5ffe667b4d1","tid":1420143,"uid":34105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco